      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist's specification, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies for instantaneous response. Power is managed through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a VANOS system refresh and rear subframe reinforcement, preserving its torsional rigidity. While it displays the honest patina of an enjoyed driver's car, the mechanical synchronization and linear power delivery remain sharp. It sits on a well-sorted suspension geometry that maintains the communicative feedback this chassis is legendary for.",
